since his return bakker said a car dealer gave him a new car 
and other offers have been made 
they told me they only have one question what can we do to 
get jim and tammy back he said never before have i had such 
an outward expression of support from local business people 
not all business owners share that sentiment 
theres still too much of a bad taste in peoples mouths 
said sharon haney who owns a small leather shop across the street 
from heritage usa 
several blocks away marge wilson who operates a craft shop 
