attempts to cure her 
eventually shes released into the custody of her childhood 
nanny margie evans who has become aunt jemima but on the plane 
on the way to her comeback in hollywood helen succumbs to her 
lingering addiction and suffers disfigurement in a bizarre pancake 
accident 
flapjack floozie also stars laraine newman marshall efron 
and toni basil and was filmed at the variety arts center an old 
vaudeville theater in los angeles the theater has surely seen 
better 
