governments massive pentagon purchasing fraud probe 
the probe has turned up rampant bribery in the government 
and includes allegations of cash payments purchase of cars and 
payments of bills for government employees sen john warner said 
wednesday 
the government is now preparing to approach people whose voices 
are recorded on the taps and who are implicated in possibly illegal 
acts said the sources speaking on condition of anonymity 
theyre going to confront them with the tapes and see who they 
can flip into becoming government witnesses one source said 
wednesday 
